  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5700039/" class="title-link">酣畅淋漓的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5700039"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ttnunu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u50120113-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ttnunu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">围观 </span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-16 00:36:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5700039_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  两天来回的飞机，没有这本书，就太没意思啦。从一战德国因为战败被整，讲到希特勒的崛起，德国在大战前的准备，以及闪电攻击波兰，干掉法国，大不列颠的英勇，意大利军队这支猪一样的队友，还有日本，美国，太爽了，从来没有这么喜欢过一本关于战争的书，期待下一本，意犹未尽呢。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5700039_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5700039_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
