  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5837410">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5837410/" class="title-link">支持袁老师的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5837410"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/56800841/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56800841-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56800841/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沉静的心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-08"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-08 07:29:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5837410_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         其实自己对战争历史并不是很感兴趣，关于战争的描写，一些地名、人名和部队番号，以及战争的进程，听起来很空洞，不形象，本书描写的战争场面很多，如果袁老师以视频的方式讲述似乎会更加精彩，但还是支持袁老师的书，这本书也比较生动的描述了二战的详细经过，使我有了...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
