            <div id="review_5837410_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5792452">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5792452/" class="title-link">战场上的国家个性更突出</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5792452"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/59691759/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u59691759-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59691759/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Eastmoon</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-26"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-26 14:45:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5792452_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  思路清晰的介绍了二战中途岛战役之前的“战争”过程。每场战役都有详细的兵力、战术、形势细节描写，喜欢战争的人可能比较有兴趣。对于我现在这种“战争白痴”来说，看这本书也不会觉得枯燥，还不错的。 但是有些内容交待的不够全面，或者说倚重倚轻的描述，容易误导我，比如说...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5792452/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
