            <div id="review_5792452_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7306470">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7306470/" class="title-link">从世界的角度看二战，但题目不妥</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7306470"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/49020270/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49020270-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49020270/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Optimus Prime</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-12-30"
      class="main-meta">2014-12-30 21:29:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7306470_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果只看这本书的内容，很难想象是出自袁腾飞之手，因为字里行间少了些玩世不恭，多了许多严肃的数字与思考。客观的说，确实降低了阅读的娱乐性，但历史本来就很严肃，这样的叙述方式，更容易让人正视历史的重要性。不过这本书的题目《战争就是这么回事儿》我个人感觉却十分不...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7306470/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7306470_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7306470_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
